gov.usgs.volcanoes.winston.in

Class StaticImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.winston.in.StaticImporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImportSAC, ImportSeed

    public abstract class StaticImporter
extends Object
    A base class for writing a static data importer for Winston. Clients just have to fill the instructions StringBuffer, implement readFile() and call process(). readFile() is responsible for creating a map that maps Winston compatible channel codes to lists of TRACEBUF-sized Waves.
    Author:
    Dan Cervelli
